Package: declare
Type: Package
Title: Optional type annotation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alex Zarebski, Chun Fung Kwok
Maintainer: Chun Fung Kwok <kcf.jackson@gmail.com>
Description: Allows user to add type annotation to a function via comments.
    The package uses a simple mechanism, and it is designed such that the 
    annotation may be "switched on and off" as one pleases. This is an 
    experiment of programming in R with stronger type. 
